{"word":"Man","slug":"man","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Man</b> - <b>(A) APPARENT INSIGNIFICANCE OF</b><p/>A tenant in a house of clay<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=4&verse=19'>Job 4:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=7&verse=17'>Job 7:17</a><p/>A worm<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=25&verse=6'>Job 25:6</a><p/>An atom in the natural universe<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=8&verse=4'>Ps 8:4</a><p/>A grasshopper when compared to God<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=40&verse=22'>Isa 40:22</a><p/>Yet under the watchful care of the Almighty<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=41&verse=14'>Isa 41:14</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Frailty, TRANSIENT<p/>Man as Grass, MORTALITY<p/><b>(B) EQUALITY OF</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=22&verse=2'>Pro 22:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=23&verse=8'>Mat 23:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10&verse=28'>Act 10:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=10&verse=12'>Rom 10:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=3&verse=28'>Gal 3:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=2&verse=5'>Jas 2:5</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Partiality Forbidden, INJUSTICE<p/>Impartiality, JUSTICE<p/> JUSTICE<p/><b>(C) MADE IN THE DIVINE IMAGE</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=26'>Gen 1:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=27'>Gen 1:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=6'>Gen 9:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=11&verse=7'>1Co 11:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=3&verse=9'>Jas 3:9</a><p/><b>(D) PRE-EMINENCE OF,</b> over other creatures<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=28'>Gen 1:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=8&verse=6'>Psa 8:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=82&verse=6'>Psa 82:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=26'>Mat 6:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=12'>Mat 12:12</a><p/><b>(E) DOMINION OF,</b> over the natural world<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=26'>Gen 1:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=2'>Gen 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=8&verse=6'>Psa 8:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=2&verse=8'>Heb 2:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=3&verse=7'>Jas 3:7</a><p/><b>(F) A SPIRITUAL BEING</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=32&verse=8'>Job 32:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=20&verse=27'>Pro 20:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=3&verse=21'>Ecc 3:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=12&verse=7'>Ecc 12:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=59'>Act 7:59</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=2&verse=11'>1Co 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=6&verse=20'>1Co 6:20</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=4&verse=16'>2Co 4:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=5&verse=23'>1Th 5:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=2&verse=26'>Jas 2:26</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Souls, IMMORTALITY<p/><b>(G) INFINITE VALUE OF,</b> seen in the price paid for his redemption<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=16'>Joh 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=6&verse=20'>1Co 6:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=1&verse=18'>1Pe 1:18-19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=5'>Rev 1:5</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Soul, LIFE"}]}